subject: Figure Skating
lead_paragraph: The Russians Yuko Kawaguchi and Alexander Smirnov edged the Canadians Jessica Dubé and Bryce Davison to win the pairs competition at Skate Canada in Ottawa. The Russians had 176.97 points to 176.54 for the Canadians, who won the free skate with a routine performed to “Carmen.”.
